{
  "id": "adv_card_aoi_51_01_short",
  "title": "井川葵 1話 莉央と愛へのドッキリ企画 (Short)",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_living-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_3d_living-01-000-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_51_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_51_01-aoi001.m4a",
      "text": "うーん……どれにしよう……\n困ったなぁ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hmm… Which one should I choose…?\nThis is tough…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 3.6666666667,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-living-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 2233.3333333000005,
          "startTime": 5.9
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_51_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_51_01-ai001.m4a",
      "text": "あれ？　葵さん、何を書いて……あ、それ『ミラクル\n☆アイドルバースデー！』のアンケートじゃないですか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Huh? Aoi-san‚ what are you writing…? Oh‚ isn't that\nthe \"Miracle ☆ Idol Birthday!\" questionnaire?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 12.3999999682,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_51_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_51_01-ai002.m4a",
      "text": "アイドルがしたいことを叶えてくれる、雑誌のお誕生日\n企画ですよね。ついに葵さんの番が来たんですね～！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's that birthday project in the magazine where they grant\nyour wishes as an idol‚ right? It's finally Aoi-san's turn~!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 18.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_51_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_51_01-aoi002.m4a",
      "text": "まぁね。でも、何を書こうか悩んでるんだ\nこころに相談して、アイデアは沢山出たんだけどね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well‚ yeah. But I'm having trouble deciding what to write.\nI've talked to Kokoro‚ and we've come up with a lot of ideas though.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 27.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_51_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_51_01-aoi003.m4a",
      "text": "例えば、「莉央にバンジージャンプをしてほしい」とか\n「莉央にぬるぬるの床の上でお相撲をしてほしい」とか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Like‚ \"I want Rio to bungee jump‚\"\nor \"I want Rio to sumo wrestle on a slippery floor.\"",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 36.0000003815,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_51_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_51_01-ai003.m4a",
      "text": "なんで莉央さんに体を張らせようとするんですか！？\nせっかくのお誕生日がギャグになっちゃいますよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Why are you trying to make Rio-san do all the physical stuff!?\nYour birthday will turn into a joke!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 43.2000026703,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_51_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_51_01-aoi004.m4a",
      "text": "でも、莉央のそんな面白……\n体を張った気高い姿が見られるのは今回くらいだよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But it would be fun… I mean‚\nThis might be the only chance to see her noble figure putting herself on the line.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 50.5000026703,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_51_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_51_01-aoi005.m4a",
      "text": "ちなみに、撮影当日に向けて練習する莉央と愛の姿を\nこころと二人で密着取材するつもりだよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "By the way‚ Kokoro and I are planning to do a close-up report on\nRio and Ai practicing for the shoot.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 59.6000026703,
      "sfxList": []
    }
  ]
}